---
import * as m from "@/paraglide/messages";
---

<!-- text part on left -->
<div
	id="processLeft"
	aria-live="polite"
	aria-atomic="true"
	class="relative flex max-h-full flex-1 flex-col items-stretch justify-stretch">
	<div class="flex flex-col gap-6 p-6">
		<p class="text-sm leading-[1.5] md:text-base md:leading-[1.8]">
			The initial phase usually consist of choosing a <span
				class="text-flatdarkviolet">design</span
			>, then deciding the additional features of websites and we will give you
			a <span class="text-flatdarkblue">budget</span> proposal.
		</p>
		<div
			class="text-sm font-normal text-muted-foreground md:text-base 2xl:text-primary/85">
			<ul class="flex list-disc flex-col gap-3 pl-2 sm:pl-4">
				<li class="sm:pl-2">
					{m.salty_red_raven_soar()}
				</li>
				<li class="sm:pl-2">
					{m.game_neat_pug_dart()}
				</li>
				<li class="sm:pl-2">
					{m.aware_wacky_eel_cry()}
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="hidden flex-col gap-6 p-6 opacity-0">
		<p class="text-sm leading-[1.5] md:text-base md:leading-[1.8]">
			The second phase is where we go to work and create a <span
				class="text-flatdarkred">prototype</span
			> of your website. We will need follow up information and data so we can populate
			the website.
		</p>
		<div
			class="text-sm font-normal text-muted-foreground md:text-base 2xl:text-primary/85">
			<ul class="flex list-disc flex-col gap-3 pl-2 sm:pl-4">
				<li class="sm:pl-2">
					{m.light_drab_hare_hush()}
				</li>
				<li class="sm:pl-2">
					{m.watery_few_mammoth_surge()}
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="hidden flex-col gap-6 p-6 opacity-0">
		<p class="text-sm leading-[1.5] md:text-base md:leading-[1.8]">
			In third phase, we will <span class="text-flatdarkgreen">optimize</span> the
			website for speed and SEO. We clean up the code and make sure the website is
			accessible and mobile friendly. Then we deploy.
		</p>
		<div
			class="text-sm font-normal text-muted-foreground md:text-base 2xl:text-primary/85">
			<ul class="flex list-disc flex-col gap-3 pl-2 sm:pl-4">
				<li class="sm:pl-2">
					{m.crazy_main_impala_pinch()}
				</li>
				<li class="sm:pl-2">
					{m.royal_slow_earthworm_bubble()}
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="hidden flex-col gap-6 p-6 opacity-0">
		<p class="text-sm leading-[1.5] md:text-base md:leading-[1.8]">
			After deploying, we will track the website's performance and exposure if
			analytics is required. We will also selectively run ad campaigns and build
			your <span class="text-flatdarkviolet">online presence</span>.
		</p>
		<div
			class="text-sm font-normal text-muted-foreground md:text-base 2xl:text-primary/85">
			{m.solid_trick_eagle_inspire()}
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
